{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1733501573.398100", "card_id": "Q_6123280263", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 310}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本 54 岁女演员中山美穗被发现「死在浴缸中」，曾主演电影《情书》，你对她有哪些印象？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据日本朝日电视台报道，日本警方 12 日 6 日称，日本女演员中山美穗被发现死在家中，终年 54 岁。 中山美穗 资料图片 据报道，当天警方接到中山美穗工作相关人士的报警称，其发现中山美穗「死在浴缸中」。随后到场的警方确认其死亡。警方正在调查其死亡原因。日媒：日本 54 岁女演员中山美穗被发现「死在浴缸中」，警方正调查死因"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-40e202fe63a4762285be74880e435b21_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "786 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6123280263"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoI7EluyG69xpEAMaCTExMjIwMTUwNCCpscq6BjAAOKgGQAByCjYxMjMyODAyNjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1733501573.400676", "card_id": "Q_6100601022", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价极客湾关于华为 mate70pro+ 的测评？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0b1c45ca7ba735d26ea869ecb970ff3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "327 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6100601022"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoI7EluyG69xpEAMaCTExMjE5Njk1MSCQnMm6BjAAOKgBQAFyCjYxMDA2MDEwMjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1733501573.400976", "card_id": "Q_6007963804", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "nigh