 / 股，上涨 24.74%。 「当前，智能驾驶领域的主流技术路线是采用多传感器融合的方法然后再去做决策，比如毫米波雷达、摄像头以及激光雷达，来实现数据的融合和处理。这种方案结合了多种传感器，旨在增强系统的冗余性和感知能力。」普华基础软件股份有限公司副总经理兼战略研究院院长张晓先在接受《每日经济新闻》记者采访时表示，当前智能驾驶的解决方案有很多，端到端的大模型纯视觉方案是新的方向，但它也有缺点，目前还不能断定它就是终极驾驶解决方案。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-385ba4c5a721c02dd8917d4b3deb196d_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6036782344"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoI7EluyG69xpEAMaCTExMjE4NDA2NiDWuMW6BjAAOIAFQBFyCjYwMzY3ODIzNDR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1733501573.413076", "card_id": "Q_2332702361", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 323}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "每天为什么不开心还坚持上班？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上班，未来"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2332702361"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoI7EluyG69xpEAMaCTExMTQ0MzI5NyCCt/y4BjAAOO0CQBJyCjIzMzI3MDIzNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1733501573.413289", "card_id": "Q_400344668", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果魏嬿婉是雍正朝的妃子，她能斗过甄嬛吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-57cb1492b08c6f95d1f810b25824f971_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/400344668"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IoI7EluyG69xpEAMaCDUxMjQ0Mjk0IO2e/PYFMAA4KUATcgk0MDAzNDQ2Njh4AKoBCWJpbGxib